getValues

public java.util.Map<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object> getValues()
Retrieves a Map of all Items within the Document. Extended by PW to use CaseInsensitiveMap.
This allows the code to deal with existing Documents or fields set via LotusScript, were the case of the Item name may be unreliable

Returns:
Map Key=Item name, Value=Item value(s)
